I use Excel for engineering spreadsheets and Microsoft Office for reports and invoices. Easier to use "ribbon" interface. This Office 2007 replaces all the standard toolbars in Office 2003. The addition of paste preview. I was using the previous version until my hard drive failed and couldn't find my software Windows 7. I was forced to purchase the 2010 version. So far I see no improvement over the previous version, but, it is early yet.
